  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium high heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the beef strips and cook until they are browned.",
    "Add the tomato paste, paprika, cumin, and cayenne pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer the mixture for 10 minutes.",
    "Fry the eggs in a separate skillet and set them aside.",
    "Season the beef mixture with salt and black pepper.",
    "To assemble the bowls, place a portion of the beef mixture in the bottom of a lacquerware bowl, followed by a fried egg.",
    "Serve the Xtra Spicy Syrian Beef Bowl immediately."
  ],
